OL,3,GBLOOPERSCITV National Weather disrupted
OL,4,Cby fault
OL,5,
OL,6,FMost of this lunchtime's ITV National
OL,7,FWeather bulletin failed to make it to
OL,8,Fair due to a technical fault.
OL,10,FITV Millbank colour bars and tone
OL,11,Fappeared immediately after the opening
OL,12,Fsponsorship sting. Within seconds this
OL,13,Fwas replaced by the "We're sorry for
OL,14,Fthe disruption" fallback loop.
OL,16,FAfter a little over 35 seconds of this
OL,17,Fwe crashed into the weather bulletin,
OL,18,Fcatching the final 12 seconds of the
OL,19,Fone-minute forecast.
OL,21,FThe cause of the fault is unclear.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
